JUST like the popular song Ibhanoyi by Blaq Diamond, Baloyi family were blessed with a brand new Toyota Quantum ya their home in Soshanguve, north of Tshwane on Saturday.  This after MEC for Public Transport and Roads Infrastructure, Jacob Mamabolo together with the Gauteng Taxi Industry leadership and SA Taxi representatives visited the family of the late Jabulani Baloyi to wish them a Merry Christmas and share some of their plans with them.  Baloyi was killed in the CBD of Tshwane during clashes between taxi operators and a group that is alleged to be participating in drug trade in the area. 